"uid":29153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:13:00.000Z","msg":"以一切必需的方式抗爭"},{"pid":"c429830b64c3af4f8f2e6f9de5a786a4f053187f","tid":1517971,"uid":247699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:14:29.000Z","msg":"體社署外抗議要求支援被捕社工<br />\n2019-08-30 HKT 10:52<br />\n <br />\n反送中社福聯合陣線早上到位於灣仔胡忠大廈的社署總部抗議，要求社署保障被捕社工、支援社工就反修例事件進行的人道救援、以及支援未成年被捕人士等。<br />\n<br />\n有社工說，至今有12名社工在衝突現場進行人道工作時以非法結集罪被捕，他認為警方做法荒謬，應該停止在有社福中心等地方施放催淚煙。<br />\n<br />\n另外，組織表示，早前有年輕示威者在深水埗被捕後，警方拒絕讓社工提供支援及陪同前往警署，他們認為此舉嚴重剝奪對未成年被捕者的支援權利，絕不能夠接受。<br />\n<br />\n現場有數十人參與，又高叫口號，要求社署署長與在場人士公開對話<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8sF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=2d95636c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1477717-20190830.htm&h=0c818935\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1477717-20190830.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n由今朝到0830到而家,署長話見又話有誠意。結果餓到我地而家係胡忠8樓,社署點解唔肯見社工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁你而家出黎未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc3ea4efa1dee7181104b110f38bbf414736ec11","tid":1517971,"uid":165665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"febb6ce2cdf9357a3025c95f34aabe532439401f","tid":1517971,"uid":255826,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a1e8c7f5accaa857cb45b5cb125487b88ca6ea2a","tid":1517971,"uid":32221,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"171c84b39958c81231f52ae1bbe50c35923f2420","tid":1517971,"uid":205482,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:51:12.000Z","msg":"行個街，講到打杖咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n萬一被包圍，齊心進攻方可保住條命去塞爆機場呀各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" c